Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:09.98,PZ,,0,0,0,,{\shad1\fs60\fn萝莉体\bord3\an8\c&HE17DCF&\pos(972,206)\3c&HFFFFFF&}我{\c&HC89C9D&}杀死了3个{\c&HAD78E9&}可爱的{\c&HC89C9D&}女生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:09.98,PZ,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\shad1\fn萝莉体\bord3\an8\c&H82CFEB&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(470.4,398.4)\4c&H000000&}但如果从这里出去 获得自由
